					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">Ah, I see the problem now (after having patched my emulator to fix another issue) - you never disabled Frame IRQs (by writing #$40, #$80, or #$C0 to $4017), so THOSE are the ones messing up your display (and being mistaken for MMC3 IRQs).</div>

					
						<div class="postbody"><br />_________________<br />Quietust, QMT Productions
<br />P.S. If you don't get this note, let me know and I'll write you another.</div>
